\p 
\v 20 \w Now|strong="G5613"\w* \w then|strong="G1722"\w*, \w since|strong="G5613"\w* \w you|strong="G1487"\w* \w died|strong="G3588"\w* \w with|strong="G1722"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* away \w from|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* basic \w principles|strong="G4747"\w* \w of|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w world|strong="G2889"\w*, \w why|strong="G5101"\w*, \w as|strong="G5613"\w* \w though|strong="G5613"\w* still \w living|strong="G2198"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w it|strong="G1487"\w*, \w are|strong="G3588"\w* \w you|strong="G1487"\w* subjecting \w yourselves|strong="G1722"\w*\f + \fr 2:20 \ft They are doing this voluntarily, but they shouldn't.\f* \w to|strong="G1722"\w* regulations
\v 21 —Don't \w handle|strong="G2345"\w*! Don't \w taste|strong="G1089"\w*! Don't \w touch|strong="G2345"\w*!—
